close_reason: "All 10 audit phases completed: security remediation, full lifecycle dogfood verification, dead code removal (15 files), code deduplication (4 files), SDK review, lazy Sentry loading (50% startup improvement), search optimization (backoff + full verification), calendar validation, agent output review, telemetry analysis (32K events, 1.4K installs), UX improvements (214 errors addressed), and governance tracking."
